<HEAD>USDA Seeking New Bugs to Wage Biological Warfare Against Pests</HEAD>
<HEAD>EDs: Subs 3rd graf, ``We're raising xxx to CORRECT spelling of Plowman's
first name, Dean sted Deal</HEAD>
