<HEAD>Spraying of Medflies Ordered in 16-Square-Mile Zone</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 4th graf, `Five of...' to UPDATE to six Medflies found,
sted five, picks up 5th graf, `Conner said...'; SUBS 11th graf,
``The bad...' to CORRECT name of environmental group. Picks up 12th
